Brief Overview: West divided up into gang territories, you start out in one of the 5 gangs. 
Boss tells you to take out gangs for various reasons, you unlock the new characters in the different gang territories. 
After beating all 5 gang territories you slowly realize none of the gangs are at fault for what your boss claimed they did.
In fact this whole time the boss has been building propane company branches on the land taken. Boss is final battle.
